Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:13.08,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:17.35,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,I came to pick you up, since it's 10 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:20.05,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oops... I totally forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:21.28,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:23.35,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, all right? I'll contact you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:42.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:55.92,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been cared for at this place since April, as a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:02.76,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or should I say, I was cared for...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:07.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yuri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:11.67,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:14.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.40,petto,husband,0,0,0,,Oh, long time no see. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:18.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:21.58,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'll see you off. You're coming back during the weekend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:23.21,petto,husband,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.48,petto,husband,0,0,0,,See you later, Ran. Be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.52,petto,ran,0,0,0,,Be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:29.72,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Goodbye, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:29.99,petto overlap,husband,0,0,0,,I should be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:31.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.87,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:44.33,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,What kind of a final night did you spend together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:47.24,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You can forget the little details,\NI just want to know the end result.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:48.87,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,As for the end result...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:56.85,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I ended up telling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.75,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I told him, "Don't go."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:04.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:24.24,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,This is bad, Momo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:26.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What I'm getting at is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.45,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I ended up doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,When I woke up, Momo was lying naked next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.52,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I ran away by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:48.16,title,text,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,140)\blur0.7}You are my pet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.16,episode,text,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,377)\blur0.6}10. Journey from paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I had planned on seeing him off with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.45,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I thought I'd have to say goodbye with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:03:00.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But it just rolled out of my mouth, "Don't go."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:04.21,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But when she told me not to go with tears in her eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:07.48,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:10.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He suddenly seemed so precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.62,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,And then the brakes just wouldn't work, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.56,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I just let everything happen naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:21.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Meaning... things just happened, one after another, in the heat of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.17,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,The heat of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, I think it was just the heat and mood of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:30.71,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because it was the last night, I think both our emotions were kind of high.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I think that's why things happened the way they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.51,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,And, why are you here right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.18,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But when I woke up, she wasn't there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:42.79,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Isn't that harsh? No letter, no breakfast, no nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:45.32,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Don't keep asking for breakfast even until the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.49,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.33,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,She's the one who told me not to go, yet she's the one who left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:52.03,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It's total abandonment. She didn't even bring her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.70,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Even though it's already time for me to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:59.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because I didn't know what kind of a face I should greet him with in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,My dignity as a pet owner is tattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.90,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Why are you talking about dignity now? That's not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.11,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You go home right now, and tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.65,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,"Are you going to pick Germany or me?! Of course me, right?!", and stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can't say such an unreasonable thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.05,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You did that last night because you still felt an attachment, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:20.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Plus, it's not right to crush a young man's illustrious future with my own selfish demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He's eight years younger than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.36,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,That's not what you were thinking when you told him not to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.63,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.83,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I might just have been used to fill Hasumi-kun's void.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo might have thought to do it just for the sake of a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:36.94,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,She might have just been playing me at the last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He could be home by now, feeling refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.31,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,How do you get such a tragic outlook on things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.78,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It still made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.19,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:55.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,We shouldn't have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.26,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,You are no longer able to believe in your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.97,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,You've lost confidence in your own attractiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:12.08,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Even relationships that have been going well can turn sour after reaching a sexual encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.98,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,It happens often. I told you to keep him off the set! Forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:24.89,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,The reason for this is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.39,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Love is an uncertain thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:32.70,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Because people are afraid of losing it,\Nthey become cowardly and servile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.03,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:41.64,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,once you eat the apple,\Nyou cannot return to paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.36,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.33,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sorry I left without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:17.31,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You were leaving... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.01,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:27.25,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I wanted to say goodbye to you,\Nbut you weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:29.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.43,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:42.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It was really fun, these past two and a half months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:46.10,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:52.64,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It was really fun. I'm glad I was found by such a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:07:00.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Right around here. That's where the box was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.92,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.69,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It was so heavy! I pulled it with all my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.16,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I can only remember it like I remember a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:10.93,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, but the soft rice was striking. It was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.73,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Be careful with your asthma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.99,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And your injury, you always push yourself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:23.24,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You shouldn't push yourself too much either, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:25.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.61,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Don't try too hard with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:32.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You act too tough as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:36.52,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,When you want to cry, it's okay to cry with someone around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:38.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm not so weak as to cry in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:42.99,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But, if you can, stay the way you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.93,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Don't change too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.31,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Make sure things go well with Hasumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.43,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll try talking to him about it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:22.33,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:28.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Me too. I'm glad I got to live with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,See you again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:36.25,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,See you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.62,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:45.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.95,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay! I'll be your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.22,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, I'm Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:23.55,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was very happy with my reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.56,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's good. It's really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:30.46,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really like having you shampoo my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.50,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:53.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I said goodbye properly. Didn't I, Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:07.56,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,With a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:32.59,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.89,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.70,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,If you're looking for Sumire-chan, she's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:47.20,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I actually wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:03.92,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:22.14,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It's fine, I'll answer anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.08,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:38.69,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,There are so many things,\NI don't know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:49.63,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,From the point that a human becomes a pet, it's beyond my understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.14,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'll say this in defense of my master...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.17,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:00.28,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I think a pet is different from a bum who just lives off someone's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:04.11,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,How are they different?\NYou were being cared for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:11.49,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, but rather than a bum...\NI think I was more like a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.76,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,A blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:15.29,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, like Linus' baby blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:21.47,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Something that's always close by, you can pull it when you want, and wipe your tears and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:25.74,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I think a pet is like an evolved form of the healing comfort which blankets exude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.81,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It's alive, and has some feelings too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:34.03,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand, but you're neither a blanket nor an animal, right?{wrong}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:35.48,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That's why I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:40.22,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,At one point, I wished I could just be a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.79,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Then I wouldn't be afraid of jealousy or loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:50.16,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But at the same time, I wouldn't be able to feel happiness, fun, nor moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:54.60,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,So that's why I thought I'd go back to being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.68,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well, that's basically it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.95,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Actually, I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:16.19,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,once thought I'd like to become a rock that lies at the bottom of the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:25.03,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It seems so cool. And on rainy days, it will roll a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.76,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,And it can be a place where little fish stop to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:33.37,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I thought that would be a much more free and meaningful existence than myself at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:38.84,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I think it was the day before I found out I got into Tokyo University.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:43.15,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That's kind of an unpleasant memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:47.35,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh... it's become such a somber topic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.55,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It may be rude of me,\Nbut I'm not going to apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:55.03,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That I lied. I don't feel like I've wronged you, Hasumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:05.07,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But I do feel sorry about the fact that I caused her to end up lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:10.71,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well... it's over, anyhow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:16.38,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Now she can become happy in a normal way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:20.42,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Although I'm sure it was going well enough until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.32,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,So..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.42,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I don't plan on breaking up with Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.16,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm actually sort of glad that she told me honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:32.26,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Because she's bad at lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:36.67,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,All this time, I kind of sensed that something was amiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:40.74,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Although I never would have guessed that the pet was a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:47.58,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It was a shock to find out that she was living with a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:54.62,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But I know that she's not so smooth as to be able to double deal and cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.19,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,As I've been watching her since she entered the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:00.99,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:03.53,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:09.03,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,And I will gradually break down the wall with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:13.44,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Eventually, I hope that we can arrive at a relationship where we can truly trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.84,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,So it was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:26.98,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You're so young, but you look as if you're tired of living life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:33.36,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess I don't even have the time to be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:40.70,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,How about what you said to me when you told me you liked her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.97,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Was that also a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.37,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:53.54,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You're young after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:59.02,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Well, don't worry, and just go do your best in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.05,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Like I need you to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.09,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,All right, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:27.38,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.15,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Then, next we can take it into the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.42,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Oh, that would be nice. Then we can include Yoshie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.52,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yoshie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.32,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Hey, kitty, aren't you glad we found a good daddy for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:57.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:08.02,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,It'll get lonely around here, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.22,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,What happened to that lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:13.92,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, I said a proper goodbye to her a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.99,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,I think she'll be able to wait if it's just three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.40,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Nah, I couldn't help but eat the apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:24.20,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,An apple from paradise which I wasn't supposed to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.17,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Why, Takeshi, don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:32.21,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,The story of mankind began from the moment they left paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:43.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm... would you like to have some coffee? You have night duty after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.39,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No, I think I'll have some beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.36,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:56.03,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I just thought that we may not be able to be honest with one another if we don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:11.85,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,For lying to you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:19.89,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No, more than the lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:26.26,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,At that time, you remember how you said you had a good relationship with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.43,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Those words kind of bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:37.47,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Exactly what kind of a relationship do you mean by a good relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:53.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I think, at the beginning, I just felt like a volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:20:00.83,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But maybe he felt that way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:05.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I really liked him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.01,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's just that two people are better than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:28.65,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And eventually, he became an indispensable existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:32.15,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,And those were not feelings of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, because he was a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:39.54,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,I realised the other day, while I was looking in the mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:44.94,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,when I'm with Junpei, I'm kind of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.54,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:51.18,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,I look happy, unlike when I was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:53.55,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Was I that much of a bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.82,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.19,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Well, I wasn't so nice either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:01.49,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I really liked you, Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:05.25,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,What do you mean? That's why you're still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:11.74,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,After three years, I'm going to be a much better woman, and I'm going to be the one who'll reject you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.04,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,After three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:19.31,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.88,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,You're late, Junpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:22.88,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,What were you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:26.65,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,About how I can't see myself three years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:29.39,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,You're going to be a world famous professional dancer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.59,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well, you'll never know what could happen in the span of three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:33.89,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:37.46,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Something else might come your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:39.93,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,The world may come to an end by that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.37,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,He's been pretty pessimistic like this since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:47.74,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Sorry, Junpei, but even if the world comes to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:50.00,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'd like to believe that friendship will never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:51.84,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:53.74,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Then me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.82,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I guess I'm childish after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:01.49,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Right now, I just got this pang of sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:05.49,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,I'm kidding, I'll beat you one of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:07.62,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Junpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:09.79,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Good luck with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.00,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:15.17,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.05,0:22:33.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't expect you to forgive me just by my apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:38.06,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But my feelings for you aren't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:44.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I've liked you since Kofu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:49.03,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:52.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:23:00.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:06.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can come to show you my true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:13.06,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,So even if distance sets us apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:19.13,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,is it all right if I still like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:33.74,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I guess I can't forgive you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:41.08,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I seriously liked you, and I believed in you. That's why I can't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:47.49,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm not mature enough to get rid of all my doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:53.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:04.15,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Of course... I deserve it, since I did such a selfish thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:05.08,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.01,0:24:07.54,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Even if I felt like I wanted to protect you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:11.72,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I don't think I want to become a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:21.22,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, umm... but I did notice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:24.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.10,0:24:28.67,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,See, you apologised again. You really don't grow up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.00,0:24:31.27,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.94,0:24:34.54,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.95,0:24:47.75,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,The next time we meet, we can just be good colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.78,0:25:14.78,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.54,0:25:39.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.38,0:25:49.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.92,0:25:59.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.85,0:26:26.05,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It may be rude of me, but I'm not going to apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.05,0:26:28.05,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I don't plan on breaking up with Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.52,0:26:34.89,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I won't apologise for lying either.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.13,0:27:15.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}At any time,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.30,0:27:18.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}the world is still revolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.57,0:27:26.54,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}However much I distress,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.85,0:27:33.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must move forward once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.22,0:27:42.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.66,0:27:44.19,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wow, so much work...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.19,0:27:47.76,petto,boss,0,0,0,,Oh, Iwaya. The cover story for next week needs to be redone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.96,0:27:49.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.87,0:27:52.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Shoot, I better submit it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.04,0:27:55.54,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,They won't look over it until the evening paper is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.44,0:27:55.64,petto overlap,man,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.64,0:27:56.64,petto,man,0,0,0,,it was decided for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.04,0:27:58.48,petto,man,0,0,0,,We're all going out for a drink tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.88,0:27:59.61,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.48,0:28:02.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not sure if I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.76,0:28:05.65,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,What?! Hey, don't say such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.65,0:28:08.87,petto,man,0,0,0,,That's right, it's also a farewell party for Fukushima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.15,0:28:10.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Farewell party?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.32,0:28:12.52,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Yes. Please come, Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.59,0:28:16.53,petto,man,0,0,0,,Well, everyone! Today's meeting place is written here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.22,0:28:23.94,announcement,text,0,0,0,,{\an8}To those who wish to seek counselling in the Counselling Room on the 14th floor:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.94,0:28:25.13,announcement,text,0,0,0,,{\an8}6/14 (Sat) – 6/18 (Wed)\NI will be out on an Employee Training Workshop
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.27,0:28:25.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Out?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.47,0:28:28.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Does he have employees?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.74,0:28:36.98,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Now that everyone is here, please raise your glass in one hand. And... TOAST!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.85,0:28:39.28,petto,boss,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.22,0:28:41.39,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.45,0:28:47.19,petto,man,0,0,0,,Do you remember that journalist from Maiasa Newspaper, Ikeuchi Noriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.19,0:28:49.43,petto,man,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, she returned to the company around the same time I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.43,0:28:52.93,petto,man,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's my age, and I heard she got divorced last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.56,0:28:57.37,petto,man,0,0,0,,And I heard she's now living with a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.37,0:28:59.60,petto,man,0,0,0,,People around her say that she owns a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.74,0:29:03.34,petto,man,0,0,0,,She takes care of everything, including food fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.34,0:29:06.18,petto,man,0,0,0,,I understand that she has expensive tastes, but that's a little absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.18,0:29:10.85,petto,boss,0,0,0,,That's the worst. That journalist is bad, but so is that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.85,0:29:14.42,petto,boss,0,0,0,,What kind of poor judgement does he have to be fed and supported by a woman? How pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.42,0:29:17.62,petto,boss,0,0,0,,I don't like it either. It mars the dignity of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.22,0:29:20.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is that really so? I think the whole idea of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.25,0:29:23.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,"because he's a man, because she's a woman" is old-fashioned in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.39,0:29:28.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,As long as they're supporting each other well, it shouldn't matter who's the one paying the living fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.63,0:29:31.34,petto,man,0,0,0,,Oh... apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.34,0:29:34.71,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true. I think it's totally okay to have a woman treat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.71,0:29:36.68,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,No way, I'd rather have a man treat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.68,0:29:39.91,petto,boss,0,0,0,,As usual, this woman ruins the spirit of the gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.08,0:29:43.65,petto,boss,0,0,0,,Although you say that, you're going to go with him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.65,0:29:45.98,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, that has already ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.98,0:29:46.88,petto,boss,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:50.62,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,You're kidding me? Already ended... do you mean you broke up with Hasumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.42,0:29:56.89,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm going to go back to the office. I still have work left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.40,0:30:01.23,petto,man,0,0,0,,See, you made her go like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.90,0:30:09.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But after I told them, I feel like something's been lifted off my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.64,0:30:15.48,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You didn't tell Hasumi-san about your pet, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.21,0:30:19.45,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Even though I intentionally didn't say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.52,0:30:23.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I couldn't hide it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.52,0:30:27.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpai and Momo, they both mean a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.16,0:30:31.56,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,There was no way I could choose between the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.83,0:30:36.77,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You should have just deceived them somehow, and worked it to your advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.94,0:30:43.37,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Maybe you're best off alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.45,0:30:50.98,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Perhaps you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.55,0:30:57.19,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I'll thank you anyway. Thanks for not saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.96,0:31:02.36,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,It's no big deal. I just didn't want to hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.83,0:31:03.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.23,0:31:05.80,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You can laugh if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.50,0:31:09.43,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,But before I knew it, I really fell for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.27,0:31:12.34,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I had the chance to say it so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.77,0:31:15.74,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.51,0:31:18.58,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I've decided now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.71,0:31:21.24,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'll go to Rio de Janeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.48,0:31:21.98,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.98,0:31:23.25,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.25,0:31:26.28,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,He's going to be feeling the hurt of a broken relationship in the lonely city of a foreign country.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.28,0:31:28.29,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,This is the biggest chance I'll ever get.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.05,0:31:37.76,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I think the unconditional feelings that I have for him now will win his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.00,0:31:43.13,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I will become happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.34,0:31:47.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.35,0:32:01.12,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,What? You're going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.86,0:32:11.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because I can't become free like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.40,0:32:15.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,so I think I'll have to be in the company of those members a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.50,0:32:19.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll try harder, so it'll become a more comfortable place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.48,0:32:34.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although everything has disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.05,0:32:39.09,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am still not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.06,0:32:46.33,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I continue living, being supported by... and at the same time, supporting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.07,0:32:56.11,petto,girl,0,0,0,,I'm so excited about Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.78,0:33:02.78,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Do you feel restless without your Chihuahua?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.31,0:33:05.03,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.85,0:33:09.99,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Are you sure you can really be happy with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.06,0:33:15.16,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Yes, I found my new job already, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.97,0:33:29.57,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Hey, over there, are the sausages all frankfurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.57,0:33:31.38,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,No, because it's the real thing. I think
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.38,0:33:33.99,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,you will be able to enjoy quite a variety of sausages.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.99,0:33:36.35,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm lucky! I wonder if they have curry there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.35,0:33:38.10,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,I haven't researched that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.10,0:33:40.85,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Why haven't you researched it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.69,0:33:44.99,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,I feel something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.26,0:33:46.99,petto,girl,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.53,0:33:52.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I went over, and saw him feigning sleep with his Noh mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.23,0:33:54.53,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm helpless without Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.53,0:33:57.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The pet got sick of me and left. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.87,0:33:59.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It seems he's going to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.67,0:34:02.61,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.65,0:34:09.71,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Momo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.85,0:34:11.45,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.15,0:34:13.15,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.56,0:34:21.86,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Umm... who...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.09,0:34:24.56,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Well... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.76,0:34:28.20,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,That's a wonderful outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.43,0:34:31.20,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.20,0:34:33.97,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Oh, a gentle smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.44,0:34:35.91,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.91,0:34:38.18,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Umm... exactly who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.68,0:34:42.35,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,The path you are about to follow is probably the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.88,0:34:45.98,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,So you should be able to go forward without doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.35,0:34:50.36,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.95,0:34:53.16,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san, we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.92,0:35:01.30,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,But if there is even the slightest possibility of regret, it is not altogether a waste to doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.43,0:35:08.45,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,People are born as small individuals,\Nand they continually wish to grow bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.45,0:35:12.21,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,They have been living their lives wishing to grow bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.88,0:35:16.65,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,But is that truly something we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.91,0:35:19.12,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,What are you anyway? Part of some cult?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.12,0:35:21.18,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,But what does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.45,0:35:26.29,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,As long as we have a free heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.46,0:35:30.86,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,we shouldn't have to fear whether we can grow bigger or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.40,0:35:35.27,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,You can spoil yourself, you can be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.70,0:35:39.24,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Because fundamentally, humans are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.11,0:35:46.34,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Although we may be weak... without stretching ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.11,0:35:52.35,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,As long as we look around us... the place that is always close to us, is actually the most precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.52,0:36:00.32,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,I hope that you too can find your one and only place in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.47,0:36:12.47,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,I wonder who that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.04,0:36:16.97,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.35,0:36:26.05,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Oh, wha— Takeshi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.35,0:36:29.42,petto,girl,0,0,0,,I know that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.12,0:36:32.59,petto,girl,0,0,0,,If I'm correct, he's a famous dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.66,0:36:35.99,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.99,0:36:36.99,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.69,0:36:43.97,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Maybe I have done something horrible for Japan's, I mean, the world's artistic culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.20,0:36:50.04,petto,girl,0,0,0,,I think it's okay to choose that one love rather than the world's culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.61,0:36:55.75,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Because it's very difficult to find your place in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.70,0:37:28.05,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I don't have money, so here is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.05,0:37:29.29,petto,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.55,0:37:29.85,petto overlap,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Where is the train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.35,0:37:30.60,petto,,0,0,0,,Oh, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.92,0:37:35.95,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.76,0:37:41.96,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.23,0:37:45.63,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Soon I'll see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.13,0:37:48.20,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.31,0:37:58.58,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.09,0:38:11.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Something about staying home is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.76,0:38:17.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, but the kitchen, bathtub, toilet... Everywhere carries memories of Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.29,0:38:19.56,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,He may be feeling just as lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.96,0:38:21.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.03,0:38:23.90,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He may be perfectly fine, and could be some German woman's pet by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.90,0:38:25.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,They seem to have nice bodies over there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.80,0:38:28.57,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,I think he's doing his dance lessons like he's supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.04,0:38:33.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't like Germany. They have beer, Beethoven, Oliver Kahn...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.28,0:38:37.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And I was just thinking how I would like to go to the hot springs for a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.78,0:38:40.08,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Hot springs? Sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.08,0:38:40.92,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.92,0:38:42.65,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I reserved a pretty nice lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.05,0:38:44.99,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You should come along next time if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.99,0:38:46.22,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.59,0:38:52.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What an eventful three months it's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.63,0:38:57.33,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You know, Ran grew 3 cm in three months!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.24,0:39:02.71,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,One season passed, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.44,0:39:07.08,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Yes, and another season is just beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.58,0:39:09.88,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You were just having a slightly longer dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.38,0:39:13.02,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.95,0:39:17.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,All right, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.47,0:39:39.14,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not a dream at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.15,0:39:44.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,because I can vividly remember Momo's kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.99,0:39:52.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,This is bad, I better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.57,0:40:03.63,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.13,0:40:06.80,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,I know this is rather sudden, but your pet got into an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.74,0:40:08.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.87,0:40:12.68,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Fortunately, it wasn't so serious as to take his life. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.85,0:40:18.64,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.52,0:40:27.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.96,0:40:31.36,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I hurt my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.60,0:40:34.06,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.83,0:40:37.73,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,will you give me a bath again?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.20,0:40:42.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.74,0:40:48.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then first off, I need to cancel my reservation at the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.11,0:41:21.21,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.42,0:41:28.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm home, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.86,0:41:34.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.26,0:41:44.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have someone whom I can show my weaknesses, and even my most embarrassing side.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.57,0:41:57.65,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because that is like a miracle, I will never let go of this hand again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.06,0:42:15.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Well, it's been a while since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.97,0:42:18.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,but every day has been passing by as if it were meant to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.90,0:42:22.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I look after his needs, while he sleeps and dances.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.54,0:42:25.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,We haven't done anything sexual since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.41,0:42:29.05,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Apparently, our relationship is a little different from lovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.85,0:42:34.38,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,but I think it may not be that of a pet and owner anymore either...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.05,0:42:37.20,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.65,0:42:39.66,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But perhaps, as we spend more time together,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.66,0:42:41.22,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,things may change gradually.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.22,0:42:43.76,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That's why it's all right. For example,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.76,0:42:48.43,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,she'll call me "Takeshi", maybe 1 out of 10 times, when she calls my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.00,0:42:51.90,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,In that way, I think it'll change gradually.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.44,0:42:55.04,petto,couselor,0,0,0,,Do you think you two will eventually become lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.34,0:42:56.71,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.18,0:43:01.55,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It may become a totally new kind of relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.85,0:43:04.88,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't really matter what she calls me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.35,0:43:10.32,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,As long as we're always together and it's comfortable, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.80,0:43:25.04,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'll take this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.60,0:43:29.97,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,May I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.97,0:43:32.27,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.94,0:43:36.78,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Fukushima-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.78,0:43:39.05,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,What, Hasumi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.05,0:43:40.82,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Wow, you surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.99,0:43:45.82,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You know, I decided to learn samba dancing in Rio de Janeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.82,0:43:47.42,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.30,0:44:02.84,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Doesn't that guy look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.51,0:44:06.18,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Really? He's in the beginner class, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.08,0:44:14.25,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Wow, your lines look good. And your joints are properly separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.55,0:44:17.59,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes, I used to do classic dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.23,0:44:27.86,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,I got a lot together. It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.13,0:44:31.65,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh, Iwaya-san. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.90,0:44:33.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello. Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.87,0:44:35.91,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Takeshi has come home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.71,0:44:37.61,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.11,0:44:43.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.45,0:44:44.65,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.28,0:44:47.65,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, don't jump on me like that. The flan will break.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.65,0:44:50.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh! Flan?! Can I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.32,0:44:51.52,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, it's for after dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.02,0:44:52.49,petto overlap,Momo,0,0,0,,Why? Can't I open it a little now?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.66,0:44:56.93,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Wow, it looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.83,0:44:59.66,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.50,0:45:02.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm... can you get me the eggs?
