Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.99,0:45:27.42,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Wait, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.55,0:45:27.66,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.50,0:45:29.26,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You have to get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.66,0:45:29.66,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,I said, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.26,0:45:31.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You have to get it out, or else it won't stop.
